{"tid":1759012,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"J19藍田選區再次想大家幫手！我要攬炒！","createTime":"2019-11-27T11:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:54:49.000Z","uid":70580,"like":200,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"5089de41356e381cbb5e32264b88e5e80b858820","tid":1759012,"uid":70580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk5o3WC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk5o3WC.jpg&h=4e653bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n森仔做唔到 我都唔要禿頭東！<br />\n你見到呢個撚樣喊到咁，你忍唔忍心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地而家希望咁多位街坊如果當日見到選舉不公或者係投票站內任何奇怪狀況的話，<br />\n可以幫手打封email去port佢！<br />\n如果夠多人port佢，係可以告佢選舉舞弊跟住DQ佢既！<br />\n<br />\n暫時收集到當日我哋可以做嘅投訴包括 ：<br />\n- 1124上樓洗樓冇申請<br />\n- 擴音器聲浪過大<br />\n- 於屋邨內使用擴音器宣傳<br />\n- 透過電話及社交媒體軟件向選民發出選舉廣告<br />\n- 不知從何取得選民資料<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何證據，請你upload上來呢度或者推上藍田任何facebook、telegram群組！<br />\n<br />\n森仔做唔到，我都要佢做唔到！<br />\n<br />\n我 要 攬 炒！<br />\n唔要日日打1823告佢個額頭反光造成光污染！<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家幫手！"},{"pid":"e468c0e651d58ddf019d4da49b0392152140bc6a","tid":1759012,"uid":120347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"推！ <br />\n<br />\n還我森仔"},{"pid":"f367779b084e5727d88ebc2aab54a772681e17b1","tid":1759012,"uid":335894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:43:28.000Z","msg":"支持，一定幫手，推啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6335f6ffa4c3e8f09c94cd376f3a9ed09d5d058","tid":1759012,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n屌你老母一定要查清楚"},{"pid":"8ea3fe14ba8e9fcbfb699100f9ce9f5380b506f8","tid":1759012,"uid":232590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"推！俾返森仔我"},{"pid":"d08d708c0a61dcb9612a75e6b70e15ea033b62ce","ti