<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地而家希望咁多位街坊如果當日見到選舉不公或者係投票站內任何奇怪狀況的話，<br />\n可以幫手打封email去port佢！<br />\n如果夠多人port佢，係可以告佢選舉舞弊跟住DQ佢既！<br />\n<br />\n暫時收集到當日我哋可以做嘅投訴包括 ：<br />\n- 1124上樓洗樓冇申請<br />\n- 擴音器聲浪過大<br />\n- 於屋邨內使用擴音器宣傳<br />\n- 透過電話及社交媒體軟件向選民發出選舉廣告<br />\n- 不知從何取得選民資料<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何證據，請你upload上來呢度或者推上藍田任何facebook、telegram群組！<br />\n<br />\n森仔做唔到，我都要佢做唔到！<br />\n<br />\n我 要 攬 炒！<br />\n唔要日日打1823告佢個額頭反光造成光污染！<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家幫手！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"我都想要藍田公海啊 陰公"},{"pid":"cfad2c03a6c2bf9afe9684fbeb85bdae4d37a486","tid":1759012,"uid":120347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"森仔雖然唔係靚仔 但係髮線都仲係度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推到森仔做到！ 唔好比佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4149bebba4b44219afb2d44d965dcf41389abbfb","tid":1759012,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6749de23d5e5a167721e9916cf17be63d5382878","tid":1759012,"uid":319616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"Email send左啦！！！你地唔係唔撚send下話？？<br />\n再講多次 有金錢問題既 可以搞眾籌 我第一個捐 <br />\n要義工既話 出個post 一定有人幫！<br />\n四千幾人投票 你唔係以為冇人會幫下話森仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n我屌你老母呀禿頭光額東<br />\n<br />\n#燃點香港全民覺醒 #呢句唔係垃圾口號<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728a0b03cc3a0c55c8451746fc2672f4164734